get-parameter-names
===================

Retrieves the argument names of a function

## Install

```
npm install get-parameter-names
```

## Usage

```js
function foo(bar, baz) {
  return bar + baz
}

var get = require('get-parameter-names')
get(foo) // = ['bar', 'baz']
```
